o longer include stuff in the `Pending*Changed` events where the removal actually failed.\r\n\r\nSplit up into several commits for easier review.\r\n\r\n### Testing\r\n\r\nManual testing in the GUI for both a pending folder and a pending device.  Removing a pending folder for all announcing devices is only possible through the API right now and has been tested via `curl`.\r\n\r\n### Screenshots\r\n\r\n![Screenshot_2021-05-26 devtest Syncthing_pendingNotNow](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6996887/119671681-403c3400-be3a-11eb-8fae-1673e8434eec.png)\r\n\r\n### Documentation\r\n\r\nSee https://github.com/syncthing/docs/pull/645 for the API description.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/7712/reactions","total_count":2,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":2,"eyes":0},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/7712/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":null}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/comments/848811465","html_url":"https://github.com/syncthing/syncthing/issues/7700#issuecomment-848811465","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/syncthing/syncthing/issues/7700","id":848811465,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDg0ODgxMTQ2NQ==","user":{"login":"acolomb","id":6996887,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY5OTY4ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6996887?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/acolomb","html_url":"https://github.com/acolomb","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/acolomb/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/acolomb/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/acolomb/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/acolomb/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/acolomb/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/acolomb/orgs","